  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Zest 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1] </span><strong>lemon</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Combine the <strong>lemon zest </strong>and <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> – these are your <strong>lemon breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Roll the <strong>zested</strong> <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Preheat the <strong>air fryer </strong>to 180°C</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1675253443301-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
