      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the leek is cooking, chop the <strong>waxy potatoes </strong>(skins on) in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a heatproof bowl, then cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top with a fork</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 4-5 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> [6-8 min]</span> or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
