        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek has softened, add the <strong>blanched peas </strong>with a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min further or until the peas are warmed through – this is your <strong>leek & peas</strong></p>",
