    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>chives </strong>finely</p><p>Once the potatoes are cooked through, add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped chives </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Mix it all together – these are your <strong>buttery chive potatoes</strong></p>",
