      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> with the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped chives</strong> – this is your <strong>lemon mayo</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
